<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当凯蒂走进教室时，所有人都转过身来盯着她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她穿着牛仔靴、牛仔裤，戴着牛仔帽。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她脖子上戴着一条围巾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的套索在哪儿，凯蒂？” 拉里问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂转头看乔伊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39173</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把友谊测定仪拿出来。” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有人在取笑人！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46412</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那也可能是朋友之间友好的玩笑。” 乔伊笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46413</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52363</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许吧！” 凯蒂说。但是，她还是不开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>午饭后，贝柔老师告诉凯蒂该她发表了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“终于到我了。” 她一边想，一边走到了教室前面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70347</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家好！” 然后，她让同学们说喜欢的运动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70348</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们来说，我把它们写到白板上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77126</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“棒球。” 卡洛斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77127</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“骑自行车。” 劳拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“游泳。” 卢克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂飞快地写着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以帮你写。” 奥利维亚说着从座位上站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97063</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“奥利维亚和凯蒂变成好朋友了。” 乔伊想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>同学们继续说着：篮球、攀岩、滑板、网球、徒步旅行、跑步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109542</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，白板就被写满了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109543</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有人提到我最喜欢的运动——跳舞！” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃！” 拉里说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124421</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一直在学习有关肌肉的知识。” 凯蒂对拉里说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“微笑时，要用到17块肌肉；</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>皱眉时，要用到43块。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132341</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，请放松，笑一笑！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132342</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>跳舞很有意思！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>来，把书桌推到后面，跳方块舞吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊走到教室前面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卢克和卡洛斯慢慢地跟着她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148234</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们是我的帮手。” 凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们教你们基本舞步。别担心，方块舞不难。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们会跳得很棒的。” 她小声对卢克和卡洛斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她知道他们不太喜欢在大家面前跳舞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，他们是好朋友，凯蒂很感谢他们帮忙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“首先，请对你的舞伴行礼。” 凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172906</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后，向左转，向右转。很简单！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得和女生们手拉手吗？” 拉里说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185094</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂假装没听见。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185095</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂和她的帮手们示范了舞步动作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有如何转圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“挽住胳膊肘转圈就行了！” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就是这样！” 凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁想跳第一支舞？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205208</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>来啊，劳拉和拉里！来啊，奥利维亚！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205209</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208597</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂让八个人站成一个方块。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208598</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你呢？” 拉里问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我？” 凯蒂说，“我是方块舞指挥！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她开始放音乐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224823</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请向你的舞伴行礼！” 音乐开始时，凯蒂喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“向左转！” 八个人手拉手开始转圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233087</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>手拉手来向左转。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233088</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235666</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>手拉手来向左转。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>手拉手来向左转。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>向前一步，朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245664</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“非常好！现在，向右转！” 凯蒂喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>手拉手来向右转。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250626</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>手拉手来向右转。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253139</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>手拉手来向右转。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253140</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256262</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>向前一步，朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在走起来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263459</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家一起，手拉手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263460</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家一起，手拉手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家一起，手拉手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>向前一步，朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“挽起胳膊，走回原处！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>转圈，转圈，回原处。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281126</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>转圈，转圈，回原处。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281127</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283628</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家一起，转一圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>向前一步，朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>音乐停止时，大家都笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真棒，凯蒂！” 贝柔老师边喊，边鼓掌，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有乔伊，你跳得真合拍！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306522</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们再跳一次，怎么样？” 凯蒂笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们弄两个方块吧！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没跳舞的同学，一起跳吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315946</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男生和女生们马上站好位置。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319757</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂一只胳膊搂着卢克，另一只胳膊搂着卡洛斯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>81</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325494</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332708</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你们俩帮忙。你们是最棒的朋友！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>